data.description: Price Improvement! Welcome to your dream home in Fayetteville, GA! This stunning 5-bedroom, 4-bathroom 4-sided brick residence on a huge unfinished basement, built in 2019, exudes modern elegance and is situated in an excellent school district, making it the ideal family home.  As you step inside, you'll be greeted by the warm and inviting atmosphere created by the beautiful hardwood floors that grace the main level. The spacious and open floor plan is perfect for both entertaining and day-to-day living. The heart of the home is the chef's kitchen, complete with granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and a large center island for casual dining.  This 4-sided brick home is in impeccable condition, with a "like new" feel that will make you feel right at home, only built in 2019. The main level features a bedroom and a full bath, providing flexibility and convenience.  The upper level is a haven of relaxation, featuring the luxurious owner's suite with a spa-like bathroom, a large walk-in closet with a separate sitting area, and three additional bedrooms with ample space. The well-appointed bathrooms throughout the house offer both style and convenience.  Outside, you'll find a charming cul-de-sac location on a level lot with a long driveway, offering plenty of parking space for guests. The backyard is ready for your personal touch, whether you're dreaming of a beautiful garden, a play area for the kids, or an outdoor oasis for relaxing and entertaining.  This Fayetteville gem is perfectly located with quick access to major attractions. Enjoy a 10-minute drive to the renowned Trilith Studios, a 25-minute commute to Hartsfield International Airport, and just 20 minutes away from Peachtree City. Nearby, you'll also find a variety of shopping, dining, and recreational options to suit your every need.  Don't miss the opportunity to make this exceptional property your new home. Schedule a showing today and experience the perfect blend of elegance, comfort, and convenience in a sought-after location. This is more than a house; it's a lifestyle waiting for you to embrace.
